caller_intent: Brandy from Alliance Insurance Services wants to change the billing method for policy number 5620636700 from agency bill to direct bill (S grade bill).
resolution_steps: Agent Maddie from Auto Owners Insurance confirmed Brandy's identity and requested her policy number.
Maddie transferred Brandy to the agency bill department voicemail system.
Brandy left a detailed voicemail message with her name, policy number, date of policy issuance, requested billing change, and contact information for callback.
knowledge_required: Understanding of Auto Owners Insurance's billing methods (agency bill vs. direct/S grade bill)
Voicemail message structure for agency bill department
systems_referenced: Auto Owners Insurance Company agency bill department
Voicemail system with account/policy number entry
summary: Brandy from Alliance Insurance contacted Auto Owners to correct a billing method error on a policy. After being transferred to voicemail, she left a detailed message explaining the issue and requested a callback. The agent verified policy details before routing the call.
